 nts (Undergraduate)\nEvent Type: Performance\nEvent Subject: Theater/Dan
 ce\nEvent Sponsor: School of Arts and Sciences\nEvent Sponsor Department
  / Area: Theatre\, Dance\, and Performance Studies department\nEvent Spo
 nsor Details: Tufts Dance Program\nRSVP Information: dance@tufts.edu\nAd
 mission/Cost: Free and Open to the Public\nEvent Contact Name: Jaclyn Wa
 guespack\nEvent Contact Email: dance@tufts.edu\nEvent Contact Phone: 617
 -627-2556\n\nTufts Dance Program faculty member Ian Berg leads a tap wor
